BT 0 g /F2 18 Tf 180.72 720 Td (A NOTE TO KIDS \(AND PARENTS!\)) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 150 710 m 462 710 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 670 Td (Dear Reader,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 648 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 626 Td (Did you know you experience about 400 different emotions EVERY DAY?) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 604 Td (That's a lot of feelings! And sometimes those feelings can be confusing,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 582 Td (scary, or overwhelming.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 560 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 538 Td (This book is your guide to understanding all those big feelings.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 516 Td (You'll learn:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 494 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 472 Td (  * What each emotion feels like in your body) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 450 Td (  * Why you have these feelings \(they all have a purpose!\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 428 Td (  * Healthy ways to manage big emotions) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 406 Td (  * Breathing exercises and calming techniques) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 384 Td (  * That you are NOT alone - everyone has these feelings!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 362 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 340 Td (Remember: There are no 'bad' emotions. Every feeling is trying to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 318 Td (tell you something important. The goal isn't to stop having feelings.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 296 Td (The goal is to understand them and choose how to respond.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 274 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 252 Td (You are braver than you believe, stronger than you seem,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 230 Td (and smarter than you think!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 208 Td () Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 186 Td (Let's explore your feelings together!) Tj ET

endstream
