BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 121.20000000000002 635 Td (Emotions are feelings that happen inside you. They affect how you thin) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 226.8 618 Td (k, act, and feel in your body.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 570 Td (Emma's STORY:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 545 Td (Emma didn't understand why some days felt sunny inside and other days) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 525 Td (felt like rain. 'Why do I feel different every day?' Emma asked Mom.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 505 Td ('Those are your emotions, sweetheart. Everyone has them. Let me teach) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 485 Td (you about the amazing world of feelings!' And so Emma's journey of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 465 Td (emotional discovery began.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 425 Td (UNDERSTANDING THIS FEELING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 400 Td (Everyone has emotions - happy, sad, angry, scared, excited, and more!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 380 Td (Emotions are not good or bad. They are just signals that tell you something) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 360 Td (important. Like a traffic light tells drivers what to do, emotions tell you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 340 Td (what is happening inside. Learning to understand your emotions is one of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 320 Td (the most important skills you will ever develop.) Tj ET

