BT 0 g /F2 22 Tf 174.0 670 Td (Anger: The Volcano Inside) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 121.20000000000002 635 Td (Anger is a normal emotion that everyone feels. It often happens when s) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 155.52 618 Td (omething seems unfair or when our boundaries are crossed.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 570 Td (Lucas's STORY:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 545 Td (Lucas slammed the door SO hard the whole house shook. 'IT'S NOT FAIR!') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 525 Td (The volcano inside was erupting. Dad came in quietly. 'I see you're) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 505 Td (really angry. That's okay. But the door didn't do anything wrong. Let's) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 485 Td (find a better way to let that anger out.' Lucas took a deep breath and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 465 Td (listened.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 425 Td (UNDERSTANDING THIS FEELING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 400 Td (Anger can feel like a volcano building up inside you. Your face might get) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 380 Td (hot, your fists might clench, and your heart beats faster. Anger isn't bad) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 360 Td (- it tells you something needs to change. But HOW you express anger matters) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 340 Td (a lot. Yelling, hitting, or breaking things hurts others and yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 320 Td (There are much better ways to let anger out safely.) Tj ET

endstream
