BT 0 g /F2 22 Tf 163.44 670 Td (Building Emotional Strength) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 121.20000000000002 635 Td (Emotional strength \(resilience\) means being able to handle difficult e) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 226.8 618 Td (motions without falling apart.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 570 Td (Caleb's STORY:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 545 Td (When Caleb didn't make the soccer team, it felt like the end of the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 525 Td (world. But then Caleb remembered all the other hard things survived:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 505 Td (moving schools, losing a pet, failing a test. 'I got through all of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 485 Td (those. I can get through this too.' That's emotional strength.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 13 Tf 72 445 Td (UNDERSTANDING THIS FEELING:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 420 Td (Building emotional strength is like building physical strength - it takes) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 400 Td (practice! Every time you face a hard emotion and get through it, you become) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 380 Td (stronger. Tools that help: talking to trusted people, journaling, exercise,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 360 Td (sleep, healthy food, breathing techniques, and positive self-talk. You have) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 340 Td (already survived 100% of your bad days - that's pretty amazing!) Tj ET

